              <span className="whitespace-nowrap">Rave<span className="text-[#00FF88]">&apos;</span>era</span> Group <span className="t…17107 chars truncated…-reveal mt-4 max-w-4xl text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.82] text-white md:text-7xl">
